sentence.text: We show that maternal biological_process variants have a significant genome-wide interaction with maternal pre-pregnancy overweight/obesity on regulation of alternative mRNA splicing, via spliceosome risk, with rs11161721 (P<sub>G × E</sub>=1.8 × 10<sup>-8</sup>; empirical P<sub>G × E</sub>=1.2 × 10<sup>-8</sup>) as the top hit.

entity.text: regulation of alternative mRNA splicing, via spliceosome
